                  <decoDesc>
                     <summary>One of a group of manuscripts of this text with similar illustrations mostly produced in the same workshop; cf. Brussels, Bibl. Royale, MSS. 9404-5 and 9347-8, and Venice, Marciana, Lat. Z. 547 (1924) (<ref target="https://catalog.hathitrust.org/Record/000468709">Pächt and Alexander</ref> ii. 118, pl. XI)</summary>
